MAJORITY of football players across the world earn exorbitant salaries, and most of them prefer to spend it on finer things - cars, jewellery and designer labels - all as a sign of power. South African football players cannot be left out as they too compete with their flashy lifestyle. Through their social media feed, most display their grand cars and those that are close to their hearts. Here's some PSL players and the cars close their hearts, either currently or those that they used to drive, or they prefer to drive. ITUMELENG KHUNE   RAMAHLWE MPHAHLELE  SIYABONGA NGEZANA  HAPPY JELE   LEBOHANG MABOE   LENNOX BACELA   BRIGHTON MHLONGO  DUMSANI ZUMA  LEBOHANG MANYAMA  HLOMPHO KEKANA 